  "keyFeatures": [
    "YouTube Music, Tidal, and JioSaavn integration",
    "AI-powered music recommendations with Gemini",
    "Hi-Res lossless audio support (up to 24-bit/192kHz FLAC)",
    "Global hotkey (Option + Space) for quick access",
    "Menu bar integration with album artwork",
    "Floating window with glassmorphism design",
